[~pvary] I have recreated the same patch for master. I had some issues getting the tests for the entire project to pass but the tests for the affected module are fine and I could get everything passing by excluding just a few tests like so:

{{  mvn test -Dtest=\!TestTxn*,\!TestExecDriver,\~TestLlapWebServices}}

So hopefully this is now good to go with patches for Hive 2.3.x and 3.1.x.
